{"tid":2399011,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"SpaceX 將負責 NASA 的 SPHEREx 太空望遠鏡發射任務","createTime":"2021-02-07T18:29:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-08T03:30:34.000Z","uid":295230,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3527bc9a259ab3aaef4be58176c6ae36dd116e61","tid":2399011,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T18:29:03.000Z","msg":"NASA 接下來比較重要的科學任務之一 SPHEREx 太空望遠鏡，現在終於確定了發射的合作方。結果沒什麼意外，仍是 Elon Musk 的 SpaceX 拿下了合同。根據雙方目前的預估，發射最快會在 2024 年 6 月進行。至於使用的火箭，則會是 SpaceX 旗下的 Falcon 9。<br />\n<br />\nSPHEREx 本身是一項為期兩年的任務，它的主要目的是利用紅外光繪製全天空地圖，以探索、了解宇宙和星系的形成過程。除此之外，SPHEREx 也會致力於在所謂的星際「培育園」裡尋找水和有機分子的蹤跡，以確定其是如何孕育出的生命要素。"},{"pid":"a51f502154c0bd8f22ef7c366f76d98ea5935ae6","tid":2399011,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T18:29:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://chinese.engadget.com/spacex-to-launch-nasa-spherex-mission-080000896.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchinese.engadget.com%2Fspacex-to-launch-nasa-spherex-mission-080000896.html&d=wuzGI5SyrIdJ%2FUQuqXTUikBBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=a092f696\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://chinese.engadget.com/spacex-to-launch-nasa-spherex-mission-080000896.html</a>"},{"pid":"b17184ba47ba631683916766ad18aa3ff929ee18","tid":2399011,"uid":24730,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T18:41:29.000Z","msg":"對TSLA 股價有冇影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7bf0ad5c01d58962e5d3f4d00084636fa18423a","tid":2399011,"uid":295230,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b17184ba47ba631683916766ad18aa3ff929ee18","tid":2399011,"uid":24730,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T18:41:29.000Z","msg":"對TSLA 股價有冇影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T18:41:57.000Z","msg":"TSLA 無火箭業務<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03